com.w2.api.engine.components.commands

Class Speaker

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.w2.api.engine.components.commands.Speaker
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RobotCommand, RobotComponent

    public final class Speaker
extends java.lang.Object
implements RobotCommand
    Instructs a Robot object what sound file to play, if it exists.
    The command is a no-op if the sound file does not exist on the robot.
